      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-300">My background includes specialist, lead, and founder roles since 2012.</p>
      <a href="/en/projects" class="mt-4 inline-flex rounded-xl bg-cyan-300 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-950 transition hover:bg-cyan-200">
